metadata.name: nŏk-tûr′nəl
metadata.description:
In the shadows I dwell,  
Eternity my only sell,  
Bloodlust I cannot quell,  
My immortal soul, a hell.

Memories of life long gone,  
A creature of the dark I've become,  
Fangs bared, eyes aglow,  
Hunting prey, my only goal.

The taste of blood on my lips,  
A rush of power as I sip,  
But the guilt, it never slips,  
Forever cursed with this grip.

A monster, they call me,  
Feared and reviled, I see,  
But in my heart, I long to be,  
A human, once again, free.
